{
  "stem": "25598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we have to take with us only what we can carry and food for three days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We-- the adults knew that other communities had been deported before us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But somehow-- one of the big tragedies of the war was that Jewish people didn't believe what's going to happen to them, or that the Germans could really do that as such a civilized country, or that the Romanians, with whom we were friends until a year ago, could do that to us.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- everybody assumed that since we were told to take food for three days, that wherever they're taking us, we're going to be back in three days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So everybody-- my-- my parents packed little suitcases and rucksacks for everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had my rucksack, which I used to take for mountain climbing, except that it was packed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this time it was very, very, very heavy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also I was dressed with everything, double or three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Like, three pair of panties, three pair of t-shirts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They weren't called t-shirts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I forgot what they were called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And two sweaters and two coats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And like, I could hardly move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the rucksack was packed really tight, so it was pretty heavy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rucksack itself was important to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember what-- no I didn't take anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't take anything, because my mother packed it with practical things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And there wasn't any room for anything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Anyway, so we went to the train station, and I had been on trains before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went to visit my aunt's city and we traveled to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I, I enjoyed being on a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
